title: The service can sell or otherwise transfer your personal data as part of a bankruptcy proceeding or other type of financial transaction.
quoteText: TinyURL may sell, transfer or otherwise share some or all of its assets in connection with a merger, acquisition, reorganization or sale of assets or in the event of bankruptcy.
